Variables can start from an alphabet or underscore _. (_x, _wehdhi3, etc)

Special Characters except _ are not allowed.  ( ! @ # $ % ^ & * ( ) { } [ ] | \ ' " : ; - + = ~ . ? / )

Some particular keywords are not allowed. (int, double, if, for, while, float, etc) these words only use as a varibles not using as a variable names but we use these words in capital letter for variable naming.

Commas or blanks are not allowed.

Variables name cannot start with a number.

